'''缬沙坦'''（{{lang-en|Valsartan|}}），是一款[[血管紧张素II受体拮抗剂|血管紧张素II受体拮抗剂]]抗高血压类药物，该药物使血管紧张素Ⅱ的I型(AT<sub>1</sub>)受体封闭，血管紧张素Ⅱ血浆濃度升高，刺激未封闭的AT<sub>2</sub>受体，同时抗衡AT<sub>1</sub>受体的作用，从而达到扩张血管降低血压的效果。<ref name='Marks2007'>{{cite web |url=http://www.medicinenet.com/valsartan/article.htm |title=Valsartan |accessdate=2010-03-04 |author=Marks JW |date=2007-02-15 |work=MedicineNet.com |publisher=MedicineNet, Inc |archive-date=2021-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420215423/https://www.medicinenet.com/valsartan/article.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在美国，缬沙坦用于治疗高血压症、充血性[[心臟衰竭|心臟衰竭]]、后[[心肌梗塞|心肌梗塞]]。<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.pharma.us.novartis.com/product/pi/pdf/diovan.pdf| title = Diovan prescribing information| publisher = Novartis| accessdate = 2011-02-04| archive-date = 2015-09-24| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924072208/http://www.pharma.us.novartis.com/product/pi/pdf/diovan.pdf| dead-url = yes}}</ref>

瑞士汽巴-嘉基公司研发生产的缬沙坦于1995年和1996年分别获得美国和欧洲的相关专利权，并于1996年7月首次在[[德国|德国]]上市，此后陆续在[[欧洲|欧洲]]、美国、[[日本|日本]]上市。<ref> {{cite web|url=http://www.thepharmaletter.com/file/37774/first-approval-of-cibas-valsartan-for-hypertension.html |title=First Approval Of Ciba's Valsartan For Hypertension |accessdate=2011-02-04 |author= |date=1996-06-03 |work=thepharmaletter.com |publisher=}}</ref> 汽巴-嘉基公司与山德士公司在1996年合并成立了[[诺华製藥|诺华製藥]]。缬沙坦具有降血压效果持久稳定，毒副作用小的特点。

==用药==
缬沙坦口服药片包括有40 mg、80 mg、160 mg或320 mg，常用剂量范围为每日40至320 mg。

在一些市场中还存在着40 mg、80 mg、160 mg剂量的缬沙坦胶囊。 


==心肌梗死的争议==
《[[英国医学杂志|英国医学杂志]]》在2004年刊登过一期，血管紧张素受体阻滞剂是否可能会增加服用者心肌梗死的风险的文章，<ref name="BMJ1">
{{cite journal| author = Verma S, Strauss M| title = Angiotensin receptor blockers and myocardial infarction| journal = [[英国医学杂志|英国医学杂志]]| volume = 329| issue = 7477| pages = 1248–9| accessdate = 2009-11-11| doi = 10.1136/bmj.329.7477.1248| pmid = 15564232| pmc = 534428|date=2004年12月}}</ref> 并于2006年在美国心脏协会的医学杂志上展开了辩论。<ref name="Circ1">
{{cite journal| author = Strauss MH, Hall AS| title = Angiotensin receptor blockers may increase risk of myocardial infarction: unraveling the ARB-MI paradox| journal = 血液循环杂志| volume = 114| issue = 8| pages = 838–54| accessdate = 2009-11-11| doi = 10.1161/CIRCULATIONAHA.105.594986| pmid = 16923768
|date=August 2006}}</ref><ref name="Circ2">
{{cite journal| author = Tsuyuki RT, McDonald MA| title = Angiotensin receptor blockers do not increase risk of myocardial infarction| journal = [[Circulation_(journal)|Circulation]]| volume = 114| issue = 8| pages = 855–60| accessdate = 2009-11-11| doi = 10.1161/CIRCULATIONAHA.105.594978| pmid = 16923769|date=August 2006}}</ref>最终也未能就血管紧张素Ⅱ受体拮抗剂类药物是否会增加的趋势心肌梗塞共识，也没有实质性的证据表明，血管紧张素Ⅱ受体拮抗剂类药物可以减少心肌梗死。

在长期应用评价（VALUE）试验中，氨氯地平较缬沙坦心肌梗死发病率更低(19%，P=0.02)，相同的降压幅度可以使减少心血管事件终点在同等水平。<ref name="Lancet1">
{{cite journal| author = Julius S, Kjeldsen SE, Weber M, ''et al.''| title = Outcomes in hypertensive patients at high cardiovascular risk treated with regimens based on valsartan or amlodipine: the VALUE randomised trial| journal = [[The_Lancet|The Lancet]]| volume = 363| issue = 9426| pages = 2022–31| accessdate = 2009-11-11| doi = 10.1016/S0140-6736(04)16451-9| pmid = 15207952|date=June 2004}}</ref>

CHARM-alternative试验显示，尽管都为[[血管紧张素II受体拮抗剂|沙坦类药物]]，缬沙坦较坎地沙坦更易引发心肌梗死(52%，p=0.025)，<ref name="Lancet2">{{cite journal| author = Granger CB, McMurray JJ, Yusuf S, ''et al.''| title = Effects of candesartan in patients with chronic heart failure and reduced left-ventricular systolic function intolerant to angiotensin-converting-enzyme inhibitors: the CHARM-Alternative trial| journal = [[The_Lancet|The Lancet]]| volume = 362| issue = 9386| pages = 772–6|accessdate = 2009-11-11| doi = 10.1016/S0140-6736(03)14284-5| pmid = 13678870|date=September 2003}}</ref>但是坎地沙坦对心力衰竭的治疗作用尚无知晓。<ref > {{cite journal| author = 刘永梅 耿光三| title = 坎地沙坦对老年陈旧性前壁心肌梗死合并心衰的疗效观察| journal = 中国老年学杂志| volume = 28| issue = | pages = | accessdate = 2011-02-04| doi =| pmid = |date=2008年8月}}</ref>

事实在，由于AT<sub>1</sub>受阻，血管紧张素受体拮抗剂会自然的通过血管紧张素AT<sub>2</sub>受体介导。不幸的是，最近的数据表明，AT<sub>2</sub>受体刺激并没有以前预计的那么对身体有益。甚至有可能在某些情况下，会有害的助长心肌纤维化和肥大，并受到动脉粥样硬化和炎症的影响。<ref name="AJH1">{{cite journal| author = Levy BI| title = How to explain the differences between renin angiotensin system modulators| journal = Am. J. Hypertens.| volume = 18| issue = 9 Pt 2| pages = 134S–141S| accessdate = 2009-11-11| doi = 10.1016/j.amjhyper.2005.05.005| pmid = 16125050
|date=September 2005}}</ref><ref name="Circ23">{{cite journal| author = Levy BI| title = Can angiotensin II type 2 receptors have deleterious effects in cardiovascular disease? Implications for therapeutic blockade of the renin-angiotensin system| journal = 血液循环杂志| volume = 109| issue = 1| pages = 8–13| accessdate = 2009-11-11| doi = 10.1161/01.CIR.0000096609.73772.C5| pmid = 14707017|date=2004年1月}}</ref><ref name="CircHyp43">{{cite journal| author = Reudelhuber TL| title = The continuing saga of the AT2 receptor: a case of the good, the bad, and the innocuous| journal = Hypertension| volume = 46| issue = 6| pages = 1261–2| accessdate = 2009-11-11| doi = 10.1161/01.HYP.0000193498.07087.83| pmid = 16286568|date=2005年11月}}</ref>

==对其他疾病的功效==
===糖尿病===
糖耐量受损的患者服用缬沙坦，可降低[[2型糖尿病|2型糖尿病]]的发病率。<ref>{{cite journal| author = McMurray JJ, Holman RR, Haffner SM, ''et al.''| title = Effect of valsartan on the incidence of diabetes and cardiovascular events| journal = [[新英格兰医学杂志|新英格兰医学杂志]]| volume = 362| issue = 16| pages = 1477–90| pmid = 20228403| doi = 10.1056/NEJMoa1001121| accessdate = 2010-04-25|date=2010年5月}}</ref> 但是，绝对风险降低很有限（每年不到1％），控制饮食，运动或服用其他药物，可能会更好地保护患者的健康。在同一研究中发现，该药物并不能减少包括死亡在内的心血管疾病的发生。换言之，就是缬沙坦并没有使糖耐量受损的患者延长生命。

===阿茲海默症===
2007年刊登在《临床研究杂志》（''Journal of Clinical Investigation''）上的一篇研究报告显示，缬沙坦对治疗与预防[[阿茲海默症|阿茲海默症]]具有一些功效，尽管这项研究只处于实验室阶段。 <ref>{{cite journal| author = Wang J, Ho L, Chen L, ''et al.''| title = Valsartan lowers brain beta-amyloid protein levels and improves spatial learning in a mouse model of Alzheimer disease| journal = J. Clin. Invest.| volume = 117| issue = 11| pages = 3393–402| url = http://content.the-jci.org/articles/view/31547| accessdate = 2009-11-11| doi = 10.1172/JCI31547| pmid = 17965777| pmc = 2040315| date = November 2007| archive-date = 2017-11-15| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171115145535/https://content.the-jci.org/articles/view/31547| dead-url = no}}</ref>

==副作用==
在一项2316名高血压患者中进行的安慰剂与代文缬沙坦对照试验中发现，缬沙坦的总不良事件发生率同安慰剂相似。孕妇不能使用该药物，在一个案例报告中，缬沙坦牵涉到一个死胎的案例。<ref name="pmid11485133">
{{cite journal| author = Briggs GG, Nageotte MP| title = Fatal fetal outcome with the combined use of valsartan and atenolol| journal = 医疗统计年报(The Annals of Pharmacotherapy)| volume = 35| issue = 7-8| pages = 859–61| year = 2001| pmid = 11485133| doi = 10.1345/aph.1A013}}</ref>
